casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Fant, Appellant, v. Tober, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Fant v. Tober (1993), 68 Ohio St.3d 117.]

(No. 93-831 Submitted October 12, 1993 Decided December 29, 1993.) Henry J. Fant, pro se. Juan Edgardo Adorno, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., AW. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. F.E. Sweeney, J., not participating.
